317
00:12:13,100 --> 00:12:14,340
Don't get physical.

318
00:12:14,340 --> 00:12:16,300
Wait for us in Jiang Shiyan's office.

319
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:17,140
I'll get something.

320
00:12:18,860 --> 00:12:20,060
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

321
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:36,420
I'll go to the café to get coffee.

322
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:37,260
Do you want anything?

323
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:39,820
A Latte, thanks.

324
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:40,820
An Americano.

325
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:42,740
Okay.

326
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:10,340
I feel like I haven't seen you in ages.

327
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:13,700
I was working overtime yesterday.

328
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:16,020
The day before yesterday,

329
00:13:16,020 --> 00:13:17,340
my mom called me over,

330
00:13:17,340 --> 00:13:18,940
