340
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:57,460
Yang.

341
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:02,420
Here.

342
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:03,860
Your latte.

343
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:05,740
- Thanks.
- Americano.

344
00:14:07,180 --> 00:14:08,700
Is coffee this fast nowadays?

345
00:14:09,580 --> 00:14:11,100
