346
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:13,860
Do you want me to slow down?

347
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:17,500
No, the timing for the coffee...

348
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:18,340
Just perfect.

349
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:19,420
Perfect.

350
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:34,620
The report on Qinglai's matter

351
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:35,980
is very well-written.

352
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:37,420
Gan.

353
00:14:37,700 --> 00:14:38,820
Your business skills

354
00:14:38,820 --> 00:14:39,980
and thoroughness in your work

355
00:14:40,660 --> 00:14:41,580
are top-notch.

356
00:14:42,220 --> 00:14:43,660
Thanks to you for the opportunity.

357
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:44,820
For trivial matters,

358
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:46,740
leave them to me. Don't worry.

359
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:49,460
When you were on sick leave,

360
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:51,140
your division was ineffective

361
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:52,180
and disorganized.

362
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:54,460
You still need to take

363
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:55,380
on this responsibility.

