372
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:12,260
and solve problems.

373
00:15:14,420 --> 00:15:15,340
Understood.

374
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:21,180
Yang.

375
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:22,740
