376
00:15:22,740 --> 00:15:24,180
Try this sausage.

377
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:25,300
So tasty.

378
00:15:26,580 --> 00:15:27,860
Yang, this clay pot rice

379
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:30,140
