380
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:31,940
Alright, that's enough.

381
00:15:31,940 --> 00:15:33,060
No. The rarest part is

382
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:34,420
the burnt rice at the bottom,

383
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:35,900
paired with pickled cabbage.

384
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,100
So refreshing.

385
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:38,740
Let me try it.

386
00:15:38,890 --> 00:15:39,740
It's amazing.

387
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:40,860
Let me mix it well.

388
00:15:40,860 --> 00:15:41,700
Come on.

389
00:15:41,780 --> 00:15:42,620
What are you doing?

390
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:43,660
I'm just trying it.

391
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:45,020
Why? If you want it, go get it.

392
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,580
What are you doing?

393
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:47,900
Don't grab my meat.

394
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:49,820
- I want a piece.
- I saved it for Yang.

395
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:51,180
Stop messing around.

396
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:52,940
Yang still has to work.

397
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:55,180
Stop acting like a child,

398
00:15:55,180 --> 00:15:56,460
fighting over food.

399
00:15:56,940 --> 00:15:57,900
Annoying.

400
00:15:58,420 --> 00:15:59,740
Is it delicious, right?

401
00:16:00,420 --> 00:16:01,260
When are you leaving?

402
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,020
