403
00:16:04,700 --> 00:16:06,260
I need to leave by 1:45.

404
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:09,300
There are over 10 minutes left.

405
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:10,140
You have time.

406
00:16:10,150 --> 00:16:10,990
Eat slowly.

407
00:16:12,180 --> 00:16:13,100
Only over 10 minutes?

408
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:13,940
It's fine.

409
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:14,900
I eat slowly.

410
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:15,740
Don't worry about me.

411
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:17,780
Go to work. I'll eat slowly here.

412
00:16:19,060 --> 00:16:20,420
It's fine. We're not busy either.

413
00:16:20,700 --> 00:16:21,620
It's lunchtime.

414
00:16:21,620 --> 00:16:23,220
People have to eat, right?

415
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:25,100
Finished my morning meetings,

416
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,780
but I have a meeting in the afternoon.

417
00:16:26,780 --> 00:16:28,220
I've scheduled a conference call

418
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:30,260
with the finance and legal teams

419
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:31,300
and the Dingshen team.

420
00:16:31,740 --> 00:16:32,660
This conference call

421
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:34,580
will last until after ten.

422
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:35,820
Another tough battle.

423
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:37,180
Do you need me there?

424
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:38,780
No need.

425
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:39,740
Aunt said

426
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:40,700
no overtime for you.

427
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:42,100
Don't just sit around at home.

428
00:16:42,260 --> 00:16:43,740
No meeting doesn't mean you're done.

429
00:16:43,740 --> 00:16:45,020
I'll promptly ask Peng Si

430
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:46,140
to sync those controversial

431
00:16:46,140 --> 00:16:47,060
clauses to you.

432
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:48,100
Keep an eye on them.

433
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:49,540
When the time comes, you need

434
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:50,460
to be on that call.

435
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,460
Got it.

436
00:16:52,180 --> 00:16:53,180
I'll join the first part

437
00:16:53,180 --> 00:16:54,460
and head back in the evening.

438
00:16:58,460 --> 00:16:59,700
You, you...

439
00:17:00,180 --> 00:17:01,220
If you want to go home,

440
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:02,220
let him start earlier.

441
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:03,500
(Tang Yang)
No overtime today.

442
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:04,620
I can accompany you.

443
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:07,300
What are you doing?

444
00:17:07,980 --> 00:17:09,420
- I want a piece.
- No way.

445
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:11,380
You're just eyeing my sausage.

446
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:13,220
Yours is so precious?

447
00:17:13,220 --> 00:17:14,780
Yang, hurry up and eat.

448
00:17:14,780 --> 00:17:15,980
I'll take you down.

449
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:17,540
Okay.

450
00:17:17,860 --> 00:17:19,220
Let's start the meeting earlier.

451
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:21,020
After it ends, I'll go accompany my mom.

452
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:22,860
I also want to start earlier.

453
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:23,780
It also depends

454
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:24,900
on their timing over there.

455
00:17:40,460 --> 00:17:41,380
Did you drive today?

456
00:17:41,660 --> 00:17:42,500
No.

457
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:44,460
I'll pick you up after work.

458
00:17:45,420 --> 00:17:46,260
Alright.

459
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:53,060
Feng and Cheng are annoying,

460
00:17:53,060 --> 00:17:54,700
occupying you while eating.

461
00:17:56,020 --> 00:17:57,180
Have you thought about

462
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:58,900
why we don't make it public?

463
00:17:58,900 --> 00:17:59,740
Why must it be

464
00:17:59,740 --> 00:18:00,700
so sneaky?

465
00:18:01,060 --> 00:18:02,580
I have thought about this.

466
00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:05,580
Why don't we just make it public?

467
00:18:06,420 --> 00:18:08,220
Let's not act impulsively.

468
00:18:08,580 --> 00:18:10,660
Let's go back and write down

469
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:11,820
all the pros and cons

470
00:18:11,980 --> 00:18:12,980
for consideration.

471
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:14,820
That makes sense.

472
00:18:16,060 --> 00:18:17,060
What are you two doing?

473
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:20,340
Waiting for the elevator.

474
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:25,220
Without pressing the button?

475
00:18:28,260 --> 00:18:29,180
I thought Tang did.

476
00:18:29,180 --> 00:18:30,500
I thought Jiang Shiyan did.

477
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:32,460
The elevator.

478
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:37,700
Where are you going?

479
00:18:38,580 --> 00:18:39,420
I'm going down.

480
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:43,580
Let's go.

481
00:18:52,220 --> 00:18:53,060
Then I'm leaving now.

482
00:18:53,500 --> 00:18:54,340
Bye-bye.

483
00:18:55,940 --> 00:18:56,780
It rubbed your feet?

484
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:00,140
It's this spot. These shoes

485
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:01,260
always rub a bit.

486
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:02,940
Alright, I'm leaving.

487
00:19:03,460 --> 00:19:04,300
Bye-bye.

488
00:19:19,820 --> 00:19:21,980
- Tang Yang, you're back.
- Yeah.

489
00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:22,820
We have a meeting.

490
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:24,820
I'm going back to get my notebook.

491
00:19:24,820 --> 00:19:25,660
Wait for me a moment.

492
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:27,660
A takeout was delivered.

493
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:29,300
I put it on your desk.

494
00:19:30,260 --> 00:19:31,100
Takeout?

495
00:19:31,860 --> 00:19:32,700
Okay.

496
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:34,180
I didn't order takeout.

497
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:56,380
Why are you grinning over there?

498
00:19:58,340 --> 00:19:59,420
Time for the meeting.

499
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:01,740
Go ahead for the elevator.

500
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:02,980
Just one minute.

501
00:20:22,860 --> 00:20:25,500
(Qinglai Art Training Project
Review Meeting)

502
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:27,180
The Qinglai's loan expansion project

503
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:29,980
is very misleading.

504
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:31,700
It failed our trust

505
00:20:32,220 --> 00:20:33,140
and almost caused

506
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:34,220
a huge amount of bad debt.

507
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:35,340
But at the same time,

508
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:36,740
we're also fortunate.

509
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:39,380
Under Mr. Gao's wise leadership,

510
00:20:39,820 --> 00:20:41,460
thanks to the efficient execution

511
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:42,700
and responsible attitude

512
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,900
of our credit audit colleagues,

513
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:46,700
we discovered the problem in time

514
00:20:46,700 --> 00:20:47,580
during the final stage

515
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:49,140
of the project and contained

516
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:50,180
the issue,

517
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:52,300
successfully avoiding bad debt.

518
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:54,060
During this period,

519
00:20:54,220 --> 00:20:55,220
Vice President Gao

520
00:20:55,220 --> 00:20:56,540
keenly identified the problem

521
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:58,260
and decisively took action,

522
00:20:58,260 --> 00:20:59,500
quickly notifying

523
00:20:59,740 --> 00:21:01,940
the police and regulatory departments

524
00:21:02,060 --> 00:21:03,940
to prevent the Qinglai Art Training

525
00:21:04,020 --> 00:21:05,820
from causing adverse social impact.

526
00:21:06,020 --> 00:21:07,340
He's made a huge contribution

527
00:21:07,780 --> 00:21:09,660
and set an excellent example

528
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:11,440
for our colleagues at CBBC.

529
00:21:20,060 --> 00:21:22,060
How did this become Mr. Gao's credit?

530
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:24,820
I heard the report was written
by Mr. Gan.

531
00:21:36,100 --> 00:21:36,940
No way.

532
00:21:37,380 --> 00:21:38,740
Six months is too long.

533
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:40,820
Right.

534
00:21:41,260 --> 00:21:42,180
On my side,

535
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:44,500
it can't exceed three months.

536
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:02,540
(Plan)
Is that all?

537
00:22:02,540 --> 00:22:03,580
Is there anything to add?

538
00:22:03,940 --> 00:22:04,900
That would be all.

539
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:06,780
Then I'll read it out.

540
00:22:08,260 --> 00:22:09,940
The benefits of making it public:

541
00:22:10,060 --> 00:22:12,020
No need to hide from everyone.

542
00:22:12,140 --> 00:22:14,060
We can date openly.

543
00:22:14,740 --> 00:22:16,460
The downsides of making it public:

544
00:22:16,700 --> 00:22:19,060
First, we'll constantly be teased

545
00:22:19,060 --> 00:22:20,020
by our friends,

546
00:22:20,100 --> 00:22:20,940
just like we used

547
00:22:20,940 --> 00:22:22,460
to tease them back then.

548
00:22:23,620 --> 00:22:26,140
Second, we won't have time to be alone.

549
00:22:26,140 --> 00:22:27,860
They'll cling to us.

550
00:22:28,460 --> 00:22:29,500
This is very important.

551
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:32,060
Feng looks for us every day
for no reason.

552
00:22:32,060 --> 00:22:33,020
If we go public,

553
00:22:33,020 --> 00:22:34,060
he won't let us go.

554
00:22:34,260 --> 00:22:35,900
Whenever we want a private date,

555
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:37,220
he'll accuse us of choosing

556
00:22:37,220 --> 00:22:38,620
love over friendship.

557
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:40,660
He'll definitely say that.

558
00:22:41,620 --> 00:22:43,020
We have too many

559
00:22:43,020 --> 00:22:43,860
mutual friends.

560
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:45,020
It's been so many years.

561
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:46,540
Once they know we're together,

562
00:22:46,860 --> 00:22:47,980
they'll keep digging

563
00:22:47,980 --> 00:22:49,100
into our gossip.

564
00:22:49,100 --> 00:22:49,940
It'll be like we have

565
00:22:49,940 --> 00:22:51,420
24-hour surveillance around us.

566
00:22:51,420 --> 00:22:53,300
Every move will be like
in a live broadcast.

567
00:22:54,700 --> 00:22:56,020
No, that's too scary.

568
00:22:57,980 --> 00:22:58,980
So...

569
00:23:01,260 --> 00:23:02,940
We absolutely cannot make it public.

570
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:05,900
Alright, the meeting is over.

571
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:06,740
Done.

572
00:23:07,540 --> 00:23:08,380
Come on.

573
00:23:11,700 --> 00:23:12,580
But

574
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:14,060
how did we find out

575
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:14,940
about Feng Weiran

576
00:23:14,940 --> 00:23:16,300
and Jiang Yanan dating?

577
00:23:16,540 --> 00:23:17,700
They were hiding it well,

578
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:19,140
