608
00:24:37,860 --> 00:24:39,300
We're old friends.

609
00:24:39,300 --> 00:24:40,300
No need for a fee.

610
00:24:40,810 --> 00:24:41,700
Don't mention money.

611
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:42,540
Alright then.

612
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:43,700
Have him give you

613
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:45,180
a portion of the shares.

614
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:46,740
Mom,

615
00:24:46,740 --> 00:24:47,980
