616
00:24:47,980 --> 00:24:48,860
Right.

617
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:52,740
Don't mention it.

618
00:24:53,540 --> 00:24:55,540
I asked him to buy movie tickets.

619
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:56,420
Your parents and I

620
00:24:56,420 --> 00:24:57,300
all went.

621
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,940
But he bought the tickets

622
00:24:59,500 --> 00:25:01,220
for 4D movies, right?

623
00:25:01,940 --> 00:25:03,100
The movie just started.

624
00:25:03,100 --> 00:25:04,700
The chair was either

625
00:25:04,860 --> 00:25:05,860
shaking like this

626
00:25:05,860 --> 00:25:06,700
or shaking like that.

627
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:07,660
Wind blowing here,

628
00:25:07,660 --> 00:25:08,540
