629
00:25:08,740 --> 00:25:10,060
How was that watching a movie?

630
00:25:10,060 --> 00:25:10,940
We couldn't stand it.

631
00:25:10,940 --> 00:25:12,780
We left halfway through.

632
00:25:14,100 --> 00:25:14,940
Jiang Shiyan,

633
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:16,220
can you please let us

634
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:18,100
