635
00:25:18,340 --> 00:25:19,740
My fault, my fault.

636
00:25:19,900 --> 00:25:21,180
It's his fault, his fault.

637
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:25,220
Have you guys eaten?

638
00:25:25,220 --> 00:25:26,060
Yes, yes.

639
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:27,180
Fish soup with dumplings.

640
00:25:28,020 --> 00:25:28,900
Smart.

641
00:25:31,220 --> 00:25:32,060
Tang,

642
00:25:32,220 --> 00:25:33,860
