to rest early too.

648
00:25:42,340 --> 00:25:43,180
- Right.
- Okay?

649
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:44,860
- Okay.
- Okay, get to work.

650
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:46,380
Mom, you go ahead.

651
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:47,220
Okay.

652
