661
00:26:46,260 --> 00:26:47,340
Mom, you hurry and rest.

662
00:26:47,340 --> 00:26:48,340
Okay, okay.

663
00:26:54,060 --> 00:26:55,540
- What to do?
- I'll confirm again.

664
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,180
Let me check.

