668
00:27:22,980 --> 00:27:24,540
- Take some for Tang.
- Of course.

669
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:26,340
It's on the table. Go ahead.

670
00:27:26,540 --> 00:27:27,660
Alright, I'll go get it.

671
00:27:29,460 --> 00:27:30,620
My old colleague

672
00:27:30,620 --> 00:27:32,220
