673
00:27:32,500 --> 00:27:33,380
Very environmental.

674
00:27:33,380 --> 00:27:34,660
Apples and pears. Come on.

675
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:36,220
Alright, I've got it all.

676
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:38,260
Mom, everything's fine. Just go rest.

677
00:27:38,260 --> 00:27:40,100
Okay, okay, you get to work.

678
00:27:58,860 --> 00:27:59,900
Oh, my.

679
00:28:00,900 --> 00:28:02,180
Aunt Yi scared my heart condition

680
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:03,100
out of me.

681
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,100
What should we do?

682
00:28:07,980 --> 00:28:09,660
How about my place tomorrow night?

683
00:28:14,620 --> 00:28:15,500
What are you watching?

684
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:16,900
Today, I want to share

685
00:28:16,900 --> 00:28:18,620
