686
00:28:18,620 --> 00:28:21,100
for concealing dark circles.

687
00:28:21,100 --> 00:28:23,220
Why does it get darker
the more you do it?

688
00:28:23,220 --> 00:28:24,740
What are you doing?

689
00:28:24,940 --> 00:28:26,420
I'm just recording for fun.

690
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:28,620
Honey,

691
00:28:28,780 --> 00:28:29,780
I went shopping

692
00:28:29,780 --> 00:28:30,820
at Joy City with Aunt.

693
00:28:30,980 --> 00:28:32,380
I bought some cosmetics

694
00:28:32,380 --> 00:28:33,460
and met a little girl.

695
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:34,900
She asked me,

696
00:28:34,910 --> 00:28:35,780
"Miss,"

697
00:28:35,780 --> 00:28:37,220
"are you a beauty blogger?"

698
00:28:38,300 --> 00:28:39,580
Then I thought

699
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:41,220
I could be a beauty blogger.

700
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:42,500
Right?

701
00:28:42,700 --> 00:28:44,100
So, I recorded one tonight,

702
00:28:44,260 --> 00:28:45,860
but I feel it's not interesting.

703
00:28:46,060 --> 00:28:47,060
Take a look for me.

704
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:47,900
Let me.

705
00:28:48,380 --> 00:28:49,220
Go ahead.

706
00:28:49,620 --> 00:28:50,860
Today, I want to share

707
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:52,780
a little trick

708
00:28:53,060 --> 00:28:55,580
for concealing dark circles.

709
00:28:55,580 --> 00:28:57,660
Why does it get darker
the more you do it?

710
00:28:57,900 --> 00:28:59,300
First, let me

711
00:28:59,300 --> 00:29:00,140
show you.

712
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,700
Didn't you say before

713
00:29:01,700 --> 00:29:03,500
you wanted to be a designer again?

714
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:05,660
Why a beauty blogger now?

715
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:07,300
Didn't I tell you I wanted

716
00:29:07,300 --> 00:29:09,060
to change my lifestyle?

717
00:29:09,220 --> 00:29:10,220
I also want

718
00:29:10,460 --> 00:29:11,860
to try something new.

719
00:29:12,940 --> 00:29:15,460
Trying new things is fine,

720
00:29:16,100 --> 00:29:17,580
but your video content

721
00:29:17,580 --> 00:29:19,020
might be a bit too monotonous.

722
00:29:19,020 --> 00:29:20,660
It's just a makeup tutorial.

723
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:23,380
There's nothing

724
00:29:23,380 --> 00:29:25,100
special and memorable.

725
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:27,780
But makeup is done

726
00:29:27,780 --> 00:29:28,940
step by step.

727
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:30,300
What's special about it?

728
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:31,580
No rush.

729
00:29:31,980 --> 00:29:33,460
Tomorrow, I'll ask the company's

730
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:34,500
promotion and planning team

731
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:36,260
to think of something for you.

732
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:37,220
Alright.

733
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:39,820
But you're special about one thing.

734
00:29:39,940 --> 00:29:40,780
What?

735
00:29:41,100 --> 00:29:42,860
You're especially pretty.

736
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:55,380
Don't get too close.

737
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:56,660
Stop here.

738
00:29:56,940 --> 00:29:58,100
I'll walk over.

739
00:29:58,660 --> 00:29:59,580
What's wrong?

740
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,740
Am I not decent enough?

741
00:30:01,860 --> 00:30:02,740
No.

742
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:04,700
I... I...

743
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:06,740
Didn't we agree not to go public?

744
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:10,980
Just teasing you.

745
00:30:12,820 --> 00:30:13,660
But

746
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:14,820
before we're dating,

747
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:16,620
didn't I often drive you to work?

748
00:30:16,620 --> 00:30:17,500
Right.

749
00:30:18,540 --> 00:30:20,900
Is this feeling guilty
about being a thief?

750
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:22,100
What do you mean?

751
00:30:22,100 --> 00:30:23,420
Are you the thief, or am I?

752
00:30:23,540 --> 00:30:25,700
Can't we be a pair of thieves?

753
00:30:26,460 --> 00:30:27,380
That sounds better.

754
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:28,740
Then I'll leave.

755
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:29,740
Wait a minute.

756
00:30:30,260 --> 00:30:31,100
No.

757
00:30:31,390 --> 00:30:32,260
I thought about it.

758
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,700
I think we can't keep doing this.

759
00:30:34,060 --> 00:30:35,100
About what?

760
00:30:35,860 --> 00:30:37,100
We can't keep living

761
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:39,140
under Aunt Yi's shadow.

762
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:41,700
Didn't we agree to go to my place?

763
00:30:41,820 --> 00:30:42,660
It's not good either.

764
00:30:42,660 --> 00:30:43,740
Ms. Zhou comes over

765
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,060
