766
00:30:45,060 --> 00:30:46,140
every few days.

767
00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:46,980
It's not safe.

768
00:30:47,180 --> 00:30:48,020
That's true.

769
00:30:48,380 --> 00:30:49,580
So, what do you want?

770
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:51,300
How about this?

771
00:30:51,340 --> 00:30:52,820
I happen to be busy

772
00:30:53,060 --> 00:30:54,380
with work lately,

773
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:55,940
so I want to rent a short-term

774
00:30:56,220 --> 00:30:57,580
apartment near Yixiu.

775
00:31:00,420 --> 00:31:01,300
Oh, right.

776
00:31:02,140 --> 00:31:03,820
It'll be easier for me to visit you.

777
00:31:03,820 --> 00:31:05,900
Mainly, it'll be easier for you

778
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:07,180
to commute to work.

779
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:08,900
Right.

780
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:09,860
There won't be Aunt Yi

781
00:31:09,860 --> 00:31:11,180
pressuring me to sleep early.

782
00:31:11,420 --> 00:31:12,620
Yes, exactly.

783
00:31:12,620 --> 00:31:13,820
That's right.

784
00:31:15,300 --> 00:31:16,300
So,

785
00:31:16,300 --> 00:31:17,740
since

786
00:31:18,100 --> 00:31:19,260
it's so convenient,

787
00:31:19,260 --> 00:31:20,580
you should just rent it.

788
00:31:20,860 --> 00:31:21,820
Right?

789
00:31:23,660 --> 00:31:24,940
I'll send you the pictures later.

790
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:25,820
I've picked some out.

791
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:28,980
No, I meant

792
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:29,900
I'd pick a few more

793
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:31,220
and send you the photos.

794
00:31:33,780 --> 00:31:34,620
Okay.

795
00:31:34,780 --> 00:31:36,460
Send me the ones you pick later.

796
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:37,300
Okay.

797
00:31:37,540 --> 00:31:38,380
I'm off now.

798
00:31:38,980 --> 00:31:39,820
May you work well.

799
00:31:41,220 --> 00:31:42,300
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

800
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:09,460
(Jiang Shiyan)

801
00:32:23,980 --> 00:32:25,340
(I Consider You a Friend)

802
00:32:25,340 --> 00:32:26,260
Okay, cut.

803
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:29,620
Nina, very good.

804
00:32:29,620 --> 00:32:31,260
Take a break. We'll change the position.

805
00:32:31,260 --> 00:32:32,100
Alright.

806
00:32:40,700 --> 00:32:41,540
Thanks, director.

807
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,090
Nina,

808
00:32:43,100 --> 00:32:44,820
