about the schedule.

809
00:32:44,820 --> 00:32:45,980
There are two more days.

810
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:48,140
By Friday, your scenes
will be wrapped up.

811
00:32:48,140 --> 00:32:49,820
Xingyue said she would book your flight.

812
00:32:49,820 --> 00:32:51,700
Do you want to return
to Beijing or Rongcheng?

813
00:32:54,740 --> 00:32:56,500
There's an event
in Beijing next Monday.

814
00:32:56,500 --> 00:32:57,660
If you fly to Beijing,

815
00:32:57,660 --> 00:32:58,700
it'll be easier.

816
00:33:06,700 --> 00:33:09,500
(When to have dinner?)

817
00:33:15,860 --> 00:33:20,940
(Cheng Hui)

818
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:22,860
(Sheng Nina)
I'm helping out with a scene.

819
00:33:22,980 --> 00:33:24,620
Two days to finish shooting.

820
00:33:25,300 --> 00:33:28,140
(Cheng Hui)
Can we have dinner this weekend?

821
00:33:29,260 --> 00:33:30,100
Sure.

822
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:31,780
I'll book a place and tell you.

823
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,780
Book my flight back to Rongcheng.

824
00:33:36,340 --> 00:33:38,780
Check it. If there are
no night scenes on Friday,

825
00:33:39,220 --> 00:33:41,460
