and leave at night.

826
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:43,500
- Alright.
- Also,

827
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:45,140
can you ask Xingyue to help me book

828
00:33:45,140 --> 00:33:46,620
that private restaurant of her friend?

829
00:33:47,780 --> 00:33:49,260
For two on Saturday night.

830
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:50,380
I'll treat someone.

831
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:51,340
Alright.

832
00:34:00,220 --> 00:34:01,060
Over here, over here.

833
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:04,940
The driver could pick you up,

834
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:05,780
but you refused.

835
00:34:06,180 --> 00:34:08,340
I'm afraid of traffic.
The subway is convenient.

836
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:10,540
Let's go up and take a look.

837
00:34:10,940 --> 00:34:11,860
I checked it out.

838
00:34:12,180 --> 00:34:13,220
Everything is the latest.

839
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:14,500
Refrigerator, microwave,

840
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:15,460
washing machine,

841
00:34:15,460 --> 00:34:16,300
and even a dryer,

842
00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:17,300
plus a dishwasher.

843
00:34:17,940 --> 00:34:19,700
You didn't already rent it, did you?

844
00:34:20,420 --> 00:34:21,940
No, I was going to surprise you,

845
00:34:22,100 --> 00:34:23,540
