846
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:24,700
We can decide later.

847
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:28,420
I have something to tell you too,

848
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:29,860
but it's not a surprise.

849
00:34:30,660 --> 00:34:32,460
You could say it's

850
00:34:32,780 --> 00:34:33,660
