851
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:41,500
I'm sorry.

852
00:34:41,940 --> 00:34:42,820
I didn't know.

853
00:34:42,820 --> 00:34:43,980
President Zhou called me over,

854
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:45,140
