855
00:34:45,140 --> 00:34:47,060
"Go to this year's New Bud training."

856
00:34:47,420 --> 00:34:48,820
He just notified me,

857
00:34:48,820 --> 00:34:49,820
not for discussion,

858
00:34:50,060 --> 00:34:52,020
so I didn't have a chance to refuse.

859
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:53,540
What's this training

860
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,780
