862
00:34:57,100 --> 00:34:59,420
They invite some bank, investment,

863
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:00,580
and market experts to come

864
00:35:00,580 --> 00:35:01,620
and give lectures.

865
00:35:01,980 --> 00:35:04,260
Gan Yiming used to do it,

866
00:35:04,700 --> 00:35:06,660
but this year, it's my turn.

867
00:35:10,260 --> 00:35:11,100
Where is it?

868
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:12,700
How long will it take?

869
00:35:13,220 --> 00:35:14,740
This year, it's in Pujiang.

870
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:16,620
I'll be going

871
00:35:17,700 --> 00:35:18,580
for three weeks.

872
00:35:23,020 --> 00:35:24,220
